[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/21/202183.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1346247","time":"2018-5-12 19:04","userId":"owd","userName":"东东","userSign":"","message":"讲道理长期的班固米用户感觉或多或少都有点楼主所说的这种“依赖症”，不用觉得这是一种不好的习惯。疯狂刷片标记，一个是时间不允许，其次我相信长期下去也会略感乏味的。为何要强迫自己看不喜欢的片子呢？所以再久而久之自然会改变的。所以根本不需要担心所说的“标记大于欣赏”。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/66/136621.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1346254","time":"2018-5-12 19:59","userId":"chrysalis","userName":"茧","userSign":"(说得很好，那么你的女朋友呢？)","message":"我好像没有这个问题<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">动画姑且会都标上，书籍的话漏记很多，音乐则是已经弃疗","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/64/346405.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1346265","time":"2018-5-12 20:19","userId":"346405","userName":"秋叶无歌","userSign":"(尽力做事。)","message":"这么恐怖的吗？","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1346269","time":"2018-5-12 20:31","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"(答えはいつも私の胸に～)","message":"没有","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1346271","time":"2018-5-12 20:35","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"标记真的对楼主没有意义吗？如果没有意义，那楼主就去寻找更有意义的方式呗。<br><br>对我而言记录还是有用的...我不通过文字，又要通过什么方式增进对作品本身的理解呢？记录本身倒也不是为了记录，可能是为了理解。我记下来一个作品可能是因为它哪里有点意思的，如果我不把它写下来，就不会仔细想，然后过段时间也说不清它哪里好哪里不好了。虽然我说话又难听见识又浅薄，还是得记。<br><br>然后比起随时可能扔的真-单机版笔记本，有这样一个数字化的记录还是好得多的。楼主担心得从获得感从看东西转移到点格子的问题我没有体会。但楼下说的口味会因为只在一个地方点格子越来越偏的问题，我觉得是切实存在的。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/42/244287.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1346270","time":"2018-5-12 20:35","userId":"muon","userName":"muon","userSign":"(Time is not your enemy, forever is)","message":"很正常<br>关系构成的逻辑是这样的：<br>先找到想尝试作品，然后标记到BGM。<br>慢慢的，变成在BGM上找作品，再去尝试。<br>最后变成在外面偶尔看见想尝试的作品结果到BGM一翻发现没有条目，于是就不想尝试了。<br><br>而且只用BGM而不习惯用豆瓣的用户就会变成偏向观看二次元作品，因为BGM的架构就是偏向这方面的...<br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">形式决定内容，冻鳗高手养成计划!<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"></span>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1346273","time":"2018-5-12 20:37","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">不怎么上豆瓣使我逐渐跑偏</span><br>还是要扩展视野啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><br>楼主说的问题我觉得不是大问题，但你说的这个问题我觉得很大。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/35/273543.jpg","floor":"#6-2","id":"1346275","time":"2018-5-12 20:39","userId":"hydrilla","userName":"黑藻","userSign":"","message":"结论：不要只活在bangumi里"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#6-3","id":"1346342","time":"2018-5-13 01:08","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">muon</span> 说: 扩展什么视野，要立志成为冻鳗高手啊</q></div><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">不拓展视野，成不了高手！</span>b38"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#6-4","id":"1346345","time":"2018-5-13 01:16","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">muon</span> 说: 二次元，由冻鳗高手来保护！</q></div>醒醒！你自己都要被放逐出二次元了！说啥胡话呢！<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#6-5","id":"1346347","time":"2018-5-13 01:21","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">muon</span> 说: 我不是高手，还是等别人吧b38</q></div>妈的，我们俩<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">神经病一般的对话</span>。<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/42/244287.jpg","floor":"#6-6","id":"1346348","time":"2018-5-13 01:22","userId":"muon","userName":"muon","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 妈的，我们俩神经病一般的对话。</q></div><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">BGM熟人日常</span>"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/16/331630.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1346272","time":"2018-5-12 20:35","userId":"wudiangongyuan","userName":"五点共圆","userSign":"(科气严重，缺乏妹子)","message":"没有这种感觉呢，我都是以欣赏的想法来观看和思考的。。。。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/04/60/46002.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1346282","time":"2018-5-12 20:58","userId":"crest","userName":"全自动共产主义实现箱","userSign":"(May the force be with you.)","message":"markthemall syndrome","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/90/349058.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1346309","time":"2018-5-12 23:08","userId":"climber","userName":"Climber","userSign":"(在你眼中能够看见我吗？)","message":"只对动画/电影有这种感觉。<br>漫画太多短的，很多时候条漫也很好看。<br>书更是，很多时候都不需要看完全部。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/69/246935.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1346335","time":"2018-5-13 00:30","userId":"246935","userName":"llxl2","userSign":"(为什么有超神作这一评价……)","message":"只要你觉得你的最终目的“看作品”没有变，我觉得就没问题，可以让人依赖也很厉害的。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211998.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1346339","time":"2018-5-13 00:50","userId":"211998","userName":"秘则为花","userSign":"(人啊，你曾经作为人活过吗？)","message":"短期刺激都是这样，快感也符合边际效益递减的规律。你拥有一项资源越多、一项资源对你的可到达性越强，那么你对这项资源的需求就越小，就越需要加大剂量来让自己维持原来的快感，就让这一切显得索然无味、无价值、无意义了。正确地做法是多出门走走，发展几项爱好，胖宅是没人权的。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#11-1","id":"1346341","time":"2018-5-13 01:07","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"看片看到一定程度发现补番动力明显下降是正常现象<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/37/33/373399.jpg","floor":"#11-2","id":"1348303","time":"2018-5-19 15:37","userId":"373399","userName":"闪耀Ene","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 看片看到一定程度发现补番动力明显下降是正常现象</q></div>难怪我追的relife新番追到现在才看完，有的干脆追着追着就忘掉了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/93/29366.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1346657","time":"2018-5-14 02:12","userId":"sgt_pepper","userName":"Sgt. Pepper","userSign":"(Hard-boiled wonderland.)","message":"以前上豆瓣的时候也是标记狂魔 有时候会觉得标记和写评语比看片更重要…的确很多东西看完也忘了 但这也促使自己去接触更多不同风格的电影 所以不觉得这过程是毫无意义的<br>后来那个账号说荒废就荒废了 现在不标记也根本无所谓 偶尔回去翻一下还会有“原来我当年是这样想的啊”的惊喜发现 所以不用担心这种依赖症…看得开心就好啦","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/83/128390.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1346677","time":"2018-5-14 06:07","userId":"128390","userName":"渐渐融化的飘雪","userSign":"","message":"就算没有豆瓣的年代，我自己也拿着小本子记录自己看过的漫画和动画……这些网站更方便了，而且可以跟人交流讨论，不是挺好的w","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/60/326025.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1346727","time":"2018-5-14 09:56","userId":"seikai","userName":"疾風迅雷のナイトハルト","userSign":"","message":"无","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/71/317169.jpg","floor":"#15","id":"1348275","time":"2018-5-19 13:02","userId":"violetletter","userName":"星之所处","userSign":"(He is Speed and I am Balance)","message":"我现在也觉得看动画不是欣赏作品，而是完成任务了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/60.gif\" smileid=\"99\" alt=\"(bgm83)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/50/15080.jpg","floor":"#16","id":"1348278","time":"2018-5-19 13:17","userId":"jackycally","userName":"Frozen_Nanaka","userSign":"(前方路漫漫。。。)","message":"点格子其乐无穷","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/37/33/373399.jpg","floor":"#17","id":"1348302","time":"2018-5-19 15:35","userId":"373399","userName":"闪耀Ene","userSign":"(我觉得我是一个长发控)","message":"我标记是因为还有可能会重温，比如突然想看欢乐向的，我就可以通过标签快速的找到。以及记录生活，这就好像在写日记一样，以后我想回顾自己的时候就可以通过这些回想起自己当时都看了什么傻不拉几的片了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/48/54847.jpg","floor":"#18","id":"1348304","time":"2018-5-19 16:15","userId":"sha1360","userName":"Pnyuu🌟","userSign":"(世界の殼を破られば、我